channel.title: Switch - NorthEast [WIP, Project]
channel.description:
That’s right, after a 2 year hiatus, I’ve returned with a new iPhone. Now, being me, I’ve already downloaded Auxy and made me a bit of a tune. However I’m not very intrigued with how it sounds just yet. Give me some tips on how to make it sound better? (Note: my being gone did make me a bit rusty, so don’t throw a whole bunch of advanced terms at me...)
https://app.auxy.co/projects/SKbnwCMawGuMHlEMQ-3toA==
Treat it with care, cuz I don’t know how active I’ll be whenever this drops. Gotta get on a plane going back to Hawaii. Thanks!
